{"data":{"conclusion":{"html":"<p>Au bon vieux temps, les choses étaient simples. Vos données résidaient dans une base de données\net votre serveur pouvait simplement les récupérer, les injecter dans un template,\npour enfin les transmettre au client.</p>\n<p>Mais les choses se sont quelque peu complexifiées.\nAujourd'hui, les applications doivent souvent savoir récupérer leur données par\nelle-mêmes afin de générer leur propre template ou composant.\nCela a donné naissance à un tout autre type d'outillage.</p>\n<p><strong>Redux</strong> est sans conteste l'une des libraries les plus utilisées,\net son taux de satisfaction de 82% démontre bien combien elle est estimée.</p>\n<p>Cependant il n'est pas improbable que tout cela soit bientôt bouleversé\npar <strong>GraphQL</strong>. Les utilisateurs de <strong>GraphQL</strong> sont passés de 5 à 20% en deux ans,\net le client de référence semble être <strong>Apollo</strong>.\nAjoutez à celà le fait que les dernières versions d'Apollo rendent maintenant l'utilisation\nde Redux optionnelle, et il ne serait pas surprenant que les résultats soient\nbien différents dans les années à venir…</p>"},"opinions":{"opinions":[{"survey_id":"2016","tools":[{"tool_id":"redux","counts":{"would_use":3436,"would_not_use":254,"interested":4205,"not_interested":980,"never_heard":1375}},{"tool_id":"graphql","counts":{"would_use":517,"would_not_use":61,"interested":4508,"not_interested":1408,"never_heard":3756}},{"tool_id":"relay","counts":{"would_use":155,"would_not_use":68,"interested":2567,"not_interested":1381,"never_heard":6079}},{"tool_id":"apollo","counts":{"would_use":137,"would_not_use":26,"interested":1133,"not_interested":690,"never_heard":8264}},{"tool_id":"mobx","counts":{"would_use":234,"would_not_use":62,"interested":1669,"not_interested":1013,"never_heard":7272}}]},{"survey_id":"2017","tools":[{"tool_id":"redux","counts":{"would_use":10703,"would_not_use":1069,"interested":8021,"not_interested":2408,"never_heard":1465}},{"tool_id":"graphql","counts":{"would_use":2788,"would_not_use":172,"interested":14205,"not_interested":2255,"never_heard":4246}},{"tool_id":"relay","counts":{"would_use":520,"would_not_use":211,"interested":5653,"not_interested":2982,"never_heard":14300}},{"tool_id":"apollo","counts":{"would_use":1257,"would_not_use":82,"interested":4682,"not_interested":1622,"never_heard":16023}},{"tool_id":"mobx","counts":{"would_use":1140,"would_not_use":318,"interested":5315,"not_interested":4177,"never_heard":12716}}]},{"survey_id":"2018","tools":[{"tool_id":"redux","counts":{"would_use":9503,"would_not_use":2073,"interested":5414,"not_interested":2330,"never_heard":834}},{"tool_id":"graphql","counts":{"would_use":4108,"would_not_use":254,"interested":12575,"not_interested":1771,"never_heard":1421}},{"tool_id":"relay","counts":{"would_use":213,"would_not_use":252,"interested":3872,"not_interested":4403,"never_heard":11387}},{"tool_id":"apollo","counts":{"would_use":2228,"would_not_use":170,"interested":7124,"not_interested":2108,"never_heard":8507}},{"tool_id":"mobx","counts":{"would_use":1126,"would_not_use":323,"interested":4280,"not_interested":5375,"never_heard":9028}}]}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"conclusion","type":"conclusion","section":"data-layer","previous":{"id":"other-libraries","type":"other-libraries","section":"data-layer","basePath":"/data-layer/other-libraries/"},"next":{"id":"back-end-frameworks","type":"section","basePath":"/back-end-frameworks/overview/"},"basePath":"/data-layer/conclusion/","locale":"fr-FR","localeLabel":"Français","localePath":"/fr"}}